data.description: +$5000 in closing costs offered by seller! Beautiful coastal craftsman style home with in ground pool and hot tub. Located in the desired original Breakfast Point with huge lot! Close to local attractions and just a mile from the beach. This home is loaded with UPGRADES! New roof in 2019. 2 x 6 construction and Energy Star Certified. Foyer provides a large space to welcome guests into your home. Center island with sink creates an area for easy food prep and a place for your family to snack or spend time together. Kitchen includes stainless appliances and custom tile backsplash. Living areas designed to be open while still giving you privacy in more formal areas. Open laundry room with plenty of space. Master bedroom on the main floor gives you easy access to the kitchen and living areas while maintaining privacy. Upstairs bedroom has vaulted ceilings and bonus room is perfect for older children about to go to college, game room, office or theater room. Step out into your personal oasis in the back yard. Newly constructed 14x32 saltwater pool with 2 waterfalls and a 6' tanning ledge, and an inground 7'x7' hot tub. Pool has LED lights and is equipped with a heater for year-round swimming. The entire backyard was designed with concrete pavers and has a screened in lanai that provides ample space for entertaining. All measurements are approx. if important please confirm.
